text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
As the Mega Fan Fest rolls around,<n>Symboli
Rudolf leads the event with her<n>usual
self-confidence, but her<n>performance is marred by<n>
uncharacteristic oversights.

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Still, she doesn't let that faze her as she<n>takes her
place in the exhibition race.

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
As Symboli Rudolf steps up to the<n>starting line,
the crowd gets ready for a<n>race worthy of the
Emperor—but her<n>showing falls far short of their<n>
expectations.

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
For a long time after, the stands are<n>filled with
muttering about her lackluster<n>performance.
